data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom townhouse is a rare end unit, providing extra privacy and a sense of exclusivity. Conveniently located in close proximity to the airport, Camp Creek Marketplace, and just under 30 minutes from the vibrant heart of Downtown Atlanta, this residence offers the perfect blend of accessibility and luxury.  Key Features:  End Unit: Enjoy the extra windows and natural light that come with being an end unit, along with the added sense of privacy.  Spacious Bedrooms: Three generously sized bedrooms offer ample space for rest and relaxation.  Modern Bathrooms: Two full bathrooms and a powder room feature modern fixtures and tasteful finishes for a touch of luxury.  Gourmet Kitchen: The well-appointed kitchen is a chef's delight, complete with stainless steel appliances, sleek countertops, and ample storage space.  Outdoor Space: A cozy patio inside a privacy fence provides the perfect spot for morning coffee or evening relaxation.  Easy Access to Transportation: Being close to the airport ensures stress-free travel, while proximity to major highways facilitates quick access to all Atlanta has to offer.  Nearby Shopping: Camp Creek Marketplace, just a stone's throw away, offers a diverse range of shopping and dining experiences.  Quick Commute: Less than 30 minutes from Downtown Atlanta, you can enjoy the city's attractions and entertainment at your convenience.This townhouse is not just a home; it's a lifestyle. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours. Ideal unit for Airbnb or investors! Rental comps are 1900 - 2000 / month. Currently tenant occupied. Not available for show.
